Enserch names Henderson COO , Langdon CFO . Enserch Exploration Inc said on Wednesday it named David Henderson its chief operating officer and Richard Langdon its chief financial officer . Henderson , 45 , replaces Gary Junco , who left the company several months ago . Henderson previously was Enserch ' s executive vice president of worldwide exploration . Langdon , 46 , replaces J . P . McCormick , who is leaving the company , Enserch said . Langdon joins the company from Pennzoil Co . 
